Package: screenshotr
Title: Helps you put screenshots into documents
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Ian",
      family = "Lyttle",
      email = "ian.lyttle@schneider-electric.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")
    ),
    person(family = "Schneider Electric", role = c("cph"))
  )
Description: The process of taking a screenshot, scaling the size, saving the file, 
  then insering a reference into a documents can be tedious. The goal of this 
  package is to automate that process as much as possible. This package contains an
  RStudio (Shuiny gadget) addin that you can use to make documenting screenshots a
  little less painful.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.2)
